<subSubSection box="[199,1326,911,938]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,152,1018]" box="[199,1326,911,938]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,320,911,937]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Remarks.</emphasis>
This new species resembles 
<taxonomicName box="[659,831,912,937]" class="Insecta" family="Histeridae" genus="Platylomalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tonkinensis">
<emphasis box="[659,831,912,937]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Pl. tonkinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but has complete marginal pronotal stria.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
